title: The Breakfast Club Talks With Yk Osiris, Dvsn and More
itunes:title: The Breakfast Club Talks With Yk Osiris, Dvsn and More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we are joined by Canadian R&B Group Dvsn, we talk about everything from relationships to their "toxic" anthems. Later on YK Osiris joins us to talk his new music and rise to fame. To close the show Charlamagne leaves us with our Thursday positive note
